<div class="wpb_wrapper">
<p>This website is dedicated to preserving and honoring the service of all U.S. Army veterans who served in this proud Regiment, which traces its lineage all the way back to World War I, to World War II, continuing through the Vietnam War, to today’s wars in Iraq and Afghanistan. We currently have hundreds of veterans listed on various files for the different battalions of the Regiment and will be adding a Guest Book feature so that visitors to this site can locate other veterans.</p>
